metadata.name: FROZEN - A moment forever frozen
metadata.description: This illustration is adapted from an original image taken by a loving daughter at a most dire moment in her father's life and journey before his death. A journey of love, sacrifice and undying dedication. Proceeds from this auction will go into offsetting part of the cost of his care, a permanent and befitting headstone and General Certificate of Education Examination scholarship for 70 deserving students to memorialize what would have been his posthumous 70th birthday on 3/01/22.
